cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM

The paper deals with the application of deep learning techniques for the diagnosis of Alzheimer's disease using medical images. This falls under the domain of computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). Additionally, the paper also discusses the identification of disease biomarkers, which could potentially fall under multimedia (cs.MM) as it involves the analysis of medical images.
